OL,3,CNovelist and literary critic Allan
OL,4,CMassie dies aged 87
OL,6,FLiterary critic, journalist and author
OL,7,FAllan Massie has died at the age of 87.
OL,9,FMassie penned dozens of books during
OL,10,Fhis life, and wrote thousands of
OL,11,Freviews over a 50-year career with The
OL,12,FScotsman.
OL,14,FHis work was internationally
OL,15,Facclaimed, particularly in France,
OL,16,Fwhere he was awarded the Knighthood of
OL,17,Fthe Order of the Arts and Letters in
OL,18,F2007.
