OL,3,CNovelist and literary critic Allan
OL,4,CMassie dies aged 87
OL,6,FIn Britain, Massie received a CBE in
OL,7,F2013, and was given the Frederick
OL,8,FNiven Literary Award and the Scottish
OL,9,FArts Council Book Award in 1980 and
OL,10,F1982 respectively.
OL,12,FMassie's son, Alex, wrote in a
OL,13,FSubstack post that his father died
OL,14,Fpeacefully on Tuesday February 3,
OL,15,Fdescribing it as a "good and gentle
OL,16,Fend to a good and gentle life, the
OL,17,Fsort of death many of many of us might
OL,18,Fwish for ourselves."
