OL,6,FAlex said that were it not for his
OL,7,Ffather's illness "he'd be writing
OL,8,Fstill", and Massie only retired from
OL,9,Fhis newspaper role in January 2026.
OL,11,FAllan Massie was born on October 16,
OL,12,F1938 in Singapore to Aberdeenshire
OL,13,Ffarmers. Shortly after his birth the
OL,14,Ffamily returned to Scotland, before
OL,15,Fhis father went again to what was then
OL,16,FBritish Malaya in 1940 to fight the
OL,17,FJapanese.
