OL,3,CNovelist and literary critic Allan
OL,4,CMassie dies aged 87
OL,6,FMassie's parents divorced after the
OL,7,Fwar - during which his father spent
OL,8,Ffour years as a prisoner of war - and
OL,9,Fhe was then raised by his mother in
OL,10,FKintore and Inverurie.
OL,12,FMassie won scholarships to study at
OL,13,Fboth Glenalmond College and Trinity
OL,14,FCollege, Cambridge, where he read
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,FHe later settled in the Scottish
OL,18,FBorders with his wife Alison and three
OL,19,Fchildren Alex, Claudia and Louis,
OL,20,Fwhere he remained for more than 40
OL,21,Fyears.
