OL,3,CNovelist and literary critic Allan
OL,4,CMassie dies aged 87
OL,6,FAlongside his novels and column for
OL,7,FThe Scotsman, Massie also wrote for a
OL,8,Fnumber of publications including The
OL,9,FSunday Times, The Scottish Daily Mail,
OL,10,FThe Wall Street Journal and The
OL,11,FSpectator.
OL,13,FHis journalistic work also covered
OL,14,Fpolitics and sports, including work on
OL,15,Fthe Dunblane massacre of 1996.
