OL,6,FFellow author Ian Rankin, whom Massie
OL,7,Fintroduced to Rankin's first editor,
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to Massie in a post on X:
OL,9,F"Allan Massie was hugely important to
OL,10,Fme. One of my very first readers and
OL,11,Fchampions.
OL,13,F"He was also an under-appreciated
OL,14,Fnovelist, a sharp but humane literary
OL,15,Fcritic, a gentleman."
